00:01:23.480 --> 00:01:24.670
[#3 = Pig, Kim Dohoon] →
[#4 = Lion, Hong Jinkyung]

00:01:24.670 --> 00:01:25.420
Lion.

00:01:25.470 --> 00:01:25.550
[#5 = Frog, Jung Hae-in] →
[#1 = Koala, Go Younjung]

00:01:25.550 --> 00:01:27.580
