00:01:48.729 --> 00:01:50.539
[Kim Dohoon. Yes, I know him.]

00:01:52.080 --> 00:01:54.130
[It's really the senior Hong Jinkyung!]

00:01:54.170 --> 00:01:57.070
[Such a pretty mouth, and handsome ears.]

00:01:57.520 --> 00:01:57.740
