00:01:57.740 --> 00:01:59.860
[I found you, my destined other half]

00:01:59.920 --> 00:02:02.620
[It's the actor, Go Younjung.]

00:02:02.780 --> 00:02:09.280
[#1 Younjung → #2 Myungsoo →
#3 Dohoon → #4 Jinkyung → #5 Hae-in]

00:02:09.380 --> 00:02:11.160
The theme of this round of gift-giving

00:02:11.160 --> 00:02:11.200
