00:02:11.200 --> 00:02:12.870
[Gift Theme: Handmade]

00:02:12.870 --> 00:02:13.850
[Handmade?]

00:02:13.850 --> 00:02:15.010
[Handmade. (Nods)]

00:02:15.010 --> 00:02:16.090
