00:03:01.720 --> 00:03:03.390
[Thorough disguise and...]

00:03:03.390 --> 00:03:03.600
Express delivery.

00:03:03.600 --> 00:03:04.460
[Realistic acting]

00:03:04.460 --> 00:03:05.950
