00:03:06.570 --> 00:03:07.840
[Hello, express delivery for you.]

00:03:08.170 --> 00:03:08.760
[Veteran Manito, Jung Hae-in]

00:03:08.760 --> 00:03:10.060
Perfect.

00:03:11.040 --> 00:03:11.960
["Something in the Rain."]
(T/N: Directly translates to)

00:03:11.960 --> 00:03:12.330
["Something in the Rain."]
("the pretty older woman who buys me meals")

00:03:12.330 --> 00:03:13.460
-That drama was popular. -Yeah.

00:03:13.460 --> 00:03:13.570
Yes.

00:03:13.570 --> 00:03:15.370
[The plan to be a perfect older woman]

00:03:15.370 --> 00:03:15.650
