00:03:24.710 --> 00:03:25.170
Excuse me, can I do some calligraphy here?

00:03:25.170 --> 00:03:27.210
[Unpredictable]

00:03:27.230 --> 00:03:27.340
[Stumbling about]

00:03:27.340 --> 00:03:29.480
