00:03:32.360 --> 00:03:33.570
[Clumsy older woman, Hong Jinkyung]

00:03:33.640 --> 00:03:35.710
[The reason I breathe? Hong Jinkyung.]

00:03:35.710 --> 00:03:37.670
[The reason I move? Hong Jinkyung.]

00:03:37.930 --> 00:03:37.950
[Obsessed with becoming the best Manito]

00:03:37.950 --> 00:03:39.990
Until tomorrow, I'll live like

00:03:40.110 --> 00:03:40.730
my mind is filled with

00:03:40.730 --> 00:03:41.310
[Audacious declaration of dedication
to preparing his gift for Jinkyung]

00:03:41.310 --> 00:03:43.110
nothing but Hong Jinkyung.

00:03:43.329 --> 00:03:43.820
Goodness.

00:03:43.820 --> 00:03:48.070
[Frustration] [Pain]

00:03:48.100 --> 00:03:48.150
[Still, never gives up!]

00:03:48.150 --> 00:03:49.150
I can do it.

00:03:49.270 --> 00:03:49.579
