he'll make it work no matter what]

00:03:49.579 --> 00:03:51.760
OMG. Kim Dohoon, you're crazy.

00:03:52.140 --> 00:03:52.160
[Obsessed with being
the perfect Manito, Kim Dohoon]

00:03:52.160 --> 00:03:53.560
