Let's buy one and share it.

00:36:37.060 --> 00:36:37.380
[Bread Myungsoo Mission;
Mangwon-dong scoopable scone shop]

00:36:37.380 --> 00:36:38.810
Thank you.

00:36:38.830 --> 00:36:38.920
[Peach Earl Grey scone;
strawberry pistachio scone]

00:36:38.920 --> 00:36:40.520
Thank you for your hard work.

00:36:42.250 --> 00:36:43.650
[(Oh)]

00:36:43.650 --> 00:36:45.310
[Come! Come!]

00:36:45.380 --> 00:36:47.090
[Haha]

00:36:49.140 --> 00:36:51.020
[Go Younjung: Can you film this for me?]

00:36:51.060 --> 00:36:53.330
[Recommended by Park Myungsoo]

00:36:53.940 --> 00:36:56.140
[Happy]

