Then, next destination.

00:36:56.510 --> 00:36:58.330
[Heading to the next bakery!]

00:36:58.550 --> 00:36:59.970
[Go straight first.]

00:37:02.180 --> 00:37:02.800
[Wow!]

00:37:03.730 --> 00:37:06.420
[What is this? A stationery shop(?)
A stationery shop]

