[Stationery heaven]

00:37:09.840 --> 00:37:10.110
Retro and sensitive vibes.

00:37:10.110 --> 00:37:12.880
[From vintage stationery
to the latest trending items]

00:37:13.110 --> 00:37:13.510
I think senior Park Myungsoo
would like this.

00:37:13.510 --> 00:37:17.060
[A time-worn,
general-store-style stationery shop]

00:37:17.270 --> 00:37:18.970
[Looks impossible to get through]

00:37:18.970 --> 00:37:22.490
[Here… feels like
no one could even get inside?]

