[Owner: Just kind of dug around.]

00:37:47.870 --> 00:37:48.000
[(Step back first)]

00:37:48.000 --> 00:37:50.660
-I'll check the far end over there.
-One moment.

00:37:53.560 --> 00:37:55.350
[Careful (thud!)]

00:37:56.390 --> 00:37:58.180
[Haha]

00:37:59.170 --> 00:38:01.150
[Watch your head here.]

