00:38:06.180 --> 00:38:08.440
-This looks like the biggest one.
-Okay.

00:38:08.700 --> 00:38:08.970
[Step back again to pay]

00:38:08.970 --> 00:38:09.790
Okay.

00:38:11.500 --> 00:38:14.460
[Careful, careful. Haha. Clatter]

00:38:14.540 --> 00:38:17.020
[A stationery maze where
"teleporting" won't work]

00:38:17.100 --> 00:38:19.260
[Heave-ho, heave-ho]

00:38:19.580 --> 00:38:20.220
[Oh!]

00:38:20.780 --> 00:38:21.380
[Oh!!]

00:38:23.370 --> 00:38:24.540
Thank you, appreciate it.

00:38:24.540 --> 00:38:26.530
[An unexpected, natural reunion
with the stationery shop from memory]

00:38:26.530 --> 00:38:28.020
Happy New Year.

00:38:29.740 --> 00:38:32.780
[Straight. I can
just go this way, right?]

00:38:34.100 --> 00:38:36.220
[Marching forward proudly]

00:38:36.460 --> 00:38:39.100
[Manito gift] [Hurry to the bakery
