00:39:05.500 --> 00:39:05.940
We still have things to do.

00:39:05.940 --> 00:39:09.740
[Despite saying that, steps forward]

00:39:10.740 --> 00:39:13.220
[I'm just checking…]

00:39:13.500 --> 00:39:15.300
