00:39:20.620 --> 00:39:22.340
[Rushes toward the Dubai chewy cookies
in front of her]

00:39:25.900 --> 00:39:28.060
[There are eight!]

00:39:28.440 --> 00:39:28.500
-I'll take seven.
-Okay.

00:39:28.500 --> 00:39:31.220
[I'll take 7!]

00:39:31.500 --> 00:39:34.500
[Out of conscience, leaves one behind
and clears the rest]

00:39:34.740 --> 00:39:37.020
[Hehe, power-shopping 7 cookies]

00:39:37.230 --> 00:39:38.320
Thank you.

00:39:38.740 --> 00:39:40.820
[Oh wow, Happy New Year(?)
Happy New Year!]

00:39:40.820 --> 00:39:43.190
[I watch your drama!] [Oh really?]

00:39:43.190 --> 00:39:44.280
Thank you.

00:39:44.700 --> 00:39:47.220
[Bows in thanks—the Dubai chewy cookies
shop owner is my fan!]

00:39:52.100 --> 00:39:54.220
[Suddenly runs off(?)]

00:39:54.580 --> 00:39:56.700
[They must have come to
