00:40:00.460 --> 00:40:02.100
[So lucky!]

00:40:02.380 --> 00:40:04.660
[Go Younjung: Wow. How did they
happen to have some left?]

00:40:04.660 --> 00:40:06.300
[(Dazed)]

00:40:06.900 --> 00:40:08.540
[Go Younjung: Film this for me!]

00:40:08.600 --> 00:40:09.700
Feels like being rich.

00:40:09.700 --> 00:40:12.420
[Dubai tycoon]

00:40:13.620 --> 00:40:15.740
[Majestic]

00:40:16.260 --> 00:40:18.900
[Even though it's off track,
