00:41:08.500 --> 00:41:10.220
[Bread Myungsoo Mission;
Yongsan charcoal-grilled bakery]

00:41:10.220 --> 00:41:11.940
[Mangwon-dong scoopable scone shop;
Mangwon-dong sea-salt bread shop]

00:41:12.980 --> 00:41:15.740
[(Careful)]

00:41:19.380 --> 00:41:21.260
[Ah… sea-salt bread!]

00:41:22.540 --> 00:41:25.260
[Bread Myungsoo Mission;
Mangwon-dong sea-salt bread shop;]

00:41:25.260 --> 00:41:27.980
