01:06:00.300 --> 01:06:01.890
[No matter how hard she looks,
she can't find the gummies...]

01:06:01.890 --> 01:06:03.740
Not here either. Not here either.

01:06:03.740 --> 01:06:06.140
[Did he forget them?
He just delivered this in person.]

01:06:07.140 --> 01:06:09.380
[Ah! I should have sent everything at once.
This won't do...]

01:06:10.060 --> 01:06:13.260
[The snack backpack hasn't been delivered yet]

01:06:13.900 --> 01:06:17.420
[New plan! New plan!]

01:06:17.700 --> 01:06:19.940
[For the second snack drop,
I can't dress as a delivery guy again.]

01:06:20.240 --> 01:06:20.740
-That was close. I almost got caught by her. -Almost got caught.

01:06:20.740 --> 01:06:22.980
[I almost got caught by her.]

01:06:23.540 --> 01:06:25.260
[I'll just drop the snack backpack there and leave!]

01:06:25.890 --> 01:06:26.100
Now, take these...

01:06:26.100 --> 01:06:29.200
[New plan: Placing it directly
at the restaurant entrance]

01:06:29.200 --> 01:06:31.000
It's clearly visible from here.

01:06:31.780 --> 01:06:33.650
[Heading out for the second gift delivery]

01:06:33.650 --> 01:06:35.310
I'll just leave it at the door.

01:06:36.940 --> 01:06:39.620
[Go Younjung: Anyway, I received it.]

01:06:39.940 --> 01:06:41.860
[Now it's my turn to give a gift.]

01:06:42.180 --> 01:06:44.220
[Go Younjung: I'm going to stake out the annex first.]

01:06:44.540 --> 01:06:46.780
[I can't wait any longer!]

01:06:47.100 --> 01:06:48.780
[Wait for me]

01:06:49.300 --> 01:06:50.060
[Thud]

01:06:51.020 --> 01:06:53.100
[I'm screwed!]

01:06:54.500 --> 01:06:54.540
[To make matters worse,
the gummies fell on the ground...]

01:06:54.540 --> 01:06:56.000
I'm screwed. I'm screwed.

01:06:56.970 --> 01:06:57.900
What should I do?

01:06:58.940 --> 01:07:02.740
[Frantically fixing it on the street]

01:07:03.820 --> 01:07:06.140
[I'm still here]

01:07:06.980 --> 01:07:11.180
[Hae-in is flustered and losing his mind]

01:07:13.540 --> 01:07:15.060
[Trotting]

01:07:18.900 --> 01:07:20.860
[Pause]

01:07:21.700 --> 01:07:25.780
[Changes direction under
the pressure
of the full-on chase]

01:07:26.580 --> 01:07:29.700
[Getting up]
[Should we head over slowly?]

01:07:31.940 --> 01:07:33.660
[Flinching]
[Jung Hae-in: Ah! You scared me.
I thought that was a real person.]

01:07:33.700 --> 01:07:35.300
[Chinese Restaurant]

01:07:38.180 --> 01:07:42.180
[Younjung slowly gets up to execute her mission]

01:07:43.140 --> 01:07:45.940
[Starting the operation]

01:07:50.500 --> 01:07:54.100
[Chinese Restaurant]
[Have to place the gift before Younjung comes out]

01:08:00.740 --> 01:08:04.940
[Sprinting away]

01:08:04.980 --> 01:08:06.700
[Chinese Restaurant]

01:08:12.100 --> 01:08:15.620
[Run first, think later]

01:08:17.260 --> 01:08:20.340
[Returned safely]

01:08:20.979 --> 01:08:25.020
[She'll see it if I leave it at the door, right?
What if... what if she doesn't see it?]

01:08:25.140 --> 01:08:28.140
[Chinese Restaurant]
[It's clearly visible]

01:08:32.779 --> 01:08:35.260
[An eye-catching appearance]

01:08:36.260 --> 01:08:36.859
[Hahaha.]

01:08:37.740 --> 01:08:42.779
[A ridiculously huge pile of snacks]

01:08:48.260 --> 01:08:52.620
[Instinctively putting it on her back]

01:08:55.779 --> 01:09:00.180
[How did he carry this?
I can't even get my arms through.]

01:09:00.779 --> 01:09:04.100
[Go Younjung: Our... hahaha... gummies...]

01:09:04.100 --> 01:09:05.779
[Go Younjung: He said he didn't know
what I liked, so he prepared all the flavors.]

01:09:05.779 --> 01:09:09.260
[He really prepared everything.]

01:09:11.100 --> 01:09:13.020
[Whoa, I'm so touched.]

01:09:13.649 --> 01:09:14.020
This is so touching. Seriously.

01:09:14.020 --> 01:09:15.710
[Even the snack backpack
is a direct hit to her taste]

01:09:15.710 --> 01:09:17.479
This is truly touching.

01:09:19.500 --> 01:09:23.580
[Gifts from Hae-in and for Myungsoo]
[Carrying the big bags to find Myungsoo!]

01:09:26.020 --> 01:09:27.899
[Happiness]

01:09:32.080 --> 01:09:32.939
What do I do?

01:09:32.939 --> 01:09:36.100
[Snacks falling helplessly]

01:09:38.859 --> 01:09:40.020
[Is this "Hansel and Gretel"?]

01:09:40.020 --> 01:09:40.640
This...

01:09:42.540 --> 01:09:43.660
[Thud]

01:09:44.939 --> 01:09:46.340
[I heard a thud!]

01:09:47.370 --> 01:09:48.220
Oh no.

01:09:48.220 --> 01:09:50.340
[The gummy rope broke]

01:09:50.580 --> 01:09:52.859
[How did this happen?]

01:09:52.859 --> 01:09:54.300
[Clatter!]

01:09:55.510 --> 01:09:55.580
No. No way.

01:09:55.580 --> 01:09:57.340
[The disassembly officially begins]

01:09:57.340 --> 01:09:58.420
This...

01:09:59.420 --> 01:10:02.300
[It keeps... haha... it keeps falling off. Hahaha.]

01:10:02.660 --> 01:10:05.740
[Ah, here. This... Oh, so this was the lid?]

01:10:06.220 --> 01:10:10.700
[Pick it up] [Pick it up]

01:10:10.820 --> 01:10:13.500
[Hahahahahaha.]

01:10:14.100 --> 01:10:16.810
[How did he think of such a novel idea... haha.]

01:10:16.810 --> 01:10:18.100
How did he think of it?

01:10:18.740 --> 01:10:22.860
[Go Younjung: But overall, it's everything I like.]
[Po*chip...]

01:10:26.340 --> 01:10:30.060
[Go Younjung: As for Po*chip, I don't like
the green ones. I like the blue ones.]

01:10:30.060 --> 01:10:31.260
[Go Younjung: I think I said that somewhere?]

01:10:31.260 --> 01:10:31.530
[Blue!]
[Source: ELLE KOREA]

01:10:31.530 --> 01:10:35.260
When it comes to Po*chip, I prefer the blue ones over the green ones.

01:10:37.700 --> 01:10:44.460
[Who is this guy? He's too much… Honestly...]

01:10:45.100 --> 01:10:46.790
[Go Younjung: But at this level,
it feels like someone who actually knows me.]

01:10:46.790 --> 01:10:49.050
It must be someone who actually knows me.

01:10:49.220 --> 01:10:52.260
[I especially love gummy strips. There's even B*B!]

01:10:52.260 --> 01:10:55.180
[Go Younjung: I've never mentioned
that B*B is delicious anywhere.]

01:10:56.420 --> 01:10:57.060
[Frog, You...]

01:10:57.060 --> 01:10:58.290
I'm right, aren't I?

01:11:00.690 --> 01:11:01.180
Let's go.

01:11:01.180 --> 01:11:02.630
[On the other side, Frog is running himself ragged]

01:11:02.630 --> 01:11:03.490
Okay.

01:11:07.460 --> 01:11:09.590
[She's a total badass!]

01:11:09.590 --> 01:11:10.790
She's a total badass.

01:11:11.820 --> 01:11:15.420
[Ah... looking back now, it really...]

01:11:15.860 --> 01:11:17.940
[It was so thrilling...]

01:11:18.440 --> 01:11:19.300
She might be a bit scary if I get caught.

01:11:19.300 --> 01:11:22.500
[Originally worried that Koala
would
be scared of the full disguise...]

01:11:23.180 --> 01:11:24.100
[Jung Hae-in: The result was completely the opposite...]

01:11:24.100 --> 01:11:27.150
[Jung Hae-in: Even with a man in a helmet
and black clothes, she dared to chase him.]

01:11:27.150 --> 01:11:28.150
Seriously.

01:11:29.380 --> 01:11:31.190
[But why did she chase me?]

01:11:31.190 --> 01:11:32.640
That's what I'm most curious about.

01:11:32.640 --> 01:11:32.820
She actually tried to catch her Guardian Angel.

01:11:32.820 --> 01:11:35.540
[I'm the Guardian Angel...]

01:11:36.180 --> 01:11:38.940
[Koala was trying to catch the Guardian Angel.
Hahaha.]

01:11:40.340 --> 01:11:43.260
[It was a close call, but anyway, I wasn't caught.]

01:11:43.540 --> 01:11:46.930
[After a quick breather, it's time
to get the third gift ready: Dubai chewy cookies]

01:11:46.930 --> 01:11:48.180
She runs really fast, though.

01:11:48.180 --> 01:11:50.260
[Constantly thinking about the way Koala ran]

01:11:54.300 --> 01:11:58.780
[Jung Hae-in: Usually, courier services ask for
the recipient's name and signature.]

01:11:59.100 --> 01:11:59.940
If I had asked for a signature, I would've been busted long ago.

01:11:59.940 --> 01:12:02.990
[If I focus too much on details,
I might get caught...]

01:12:02.990 --> 01:12:03.850
100%.

01:12:04.820 --> 01:12:05.060
I'll be screwed.

01:12:05.060 --> 01:12:09.140
[Thrilling]

01:12:10.020 --> 01:12:12.190
[Jung Hae-in: Meeting at HQ tomorrow
will be hilarious.]

01:12:12.190 --> 01:12:13.290
Because I know everything—

01:12:13.290 --> 01:12:13.620
Her energy and her movements.

01:12:13.620 --> 01:12:16.110
[Only I know Koala's tough side]

01:12:16.110 --> 01:12:17.770
And that she's a total badass.

01:12:18.140 --> 01:12:21.500
[Pretending I don't know...
that scene will be so funny.]

01:12:22.580 --> 01:12:26.820
[But I hope she likes the gift.]

01:12:26.890 --> 01:12:27.840
Wait. Hold on.

01:12:28.460 --> 01:12:30.100
[Let me check the Polar Bear's location.]

01:12:30.100 --> 01:12:30.430
[Park Myungsoo] [Go Younjung]
[Polar Bear is still in the same spot]

01:12:30.430 --> 01:12:32.560
It seems he's still in the same place.

01:12:34.300 --> 01:12:37.500
[Recording is nearing the end]

01:12:37.860 --> 01:12:40.380
[Go Younjung: If I can't get into the annex,
how about checking the entrance?]

01:12:40.620 --> 01:12:40.810
[Heading to the entrance where Myungsoo will appear]

01:12:40.810 --> 01:12:42.400
Ah, go straight.

01:12:44.420 --> 01:12:45.620
[? Hello.]

01:12:45.750 --> 01:12:45.820
Hello. Hello.

01:12:45.820 --> 01:12:48.460
[Accidentally running into Jun Hyunmoo]

01:12:49.020 --> 01:12:50.580
[Our drama is airing!]

01:12:50.780 --> 01:12:51.220
I'm currently watching it.

01:12:51.220 --> 01:12:52.050
[The two exchange a brief greeting]

01:12:52.050 --> 01:12:53.510
The episode I filmed with you aired.

01:12:53.510 --> 01:12:54.220
Exactly.

01:12:54.500 --> 01:12:55.620
[But what are you doing?]

01:12:55.790 --> 01:12:55.900
That's a secret.

01:12:55.900 --> 01:12:56.660
[Total secrecy]

01:12:56.660 --> 01:12:57.920
-It's a secret? -Yeah.

01:12:57.940 --> 01:12:58.060
-Good luck. -Take care.

01:12:58.060 --> 01:13:04.860
[After a brief chat, back to finding Myungsoo]

01:13:07.900 --> 01:13:10.820
[Sudden panic]

01:13:10.880 --> 01:13:11.220
Wait a second.

01:13:11.220 --> 01:13:14.540
[Myungsoo and Hyunmoo are recording the same show]
[Source: SM C&C]

01:13:14.540 --> 01:13:15.220
Yeah.

01:13:15.220 --> 01:13:16.060
[But Hyunmoo is outside!]

01:13:16.060 --> 01:13:17.390
-Good luck. -Take care.

01:13:18.100 --> 01:13:22.060
[Preparing the disguise]
[It seems Myungsoo is coming out soon, too]

01:13:22.260 --> 01:13:24.980
[The building where Myungsoo is]

01:13:25.500 --> 01:13:29.260
[Staying alert just in case of a run-in]

01:13:29.260 --> 01:13:33.380
[Park Myungsoo] [Go Younjung]
[The Polar Bear starts moving now]

01:13:34.060 --> 01:13:38.340
[Luckily, Younjung came out first]

01:13:39.180 --> 01:13:41.940
[Frantic]

01:13:42.460 --> 01:13:44.940
[The symbol of the Manito gift]

01:13:45.260 --> 01:13:48.140
[Even the stickers are applied!]

01:13:50.180 --> 01:13:53.220
[I can't see what's in front of me!]

01:13:54.180 --> 01:13:56.740
[Go Younjung: You can't tell who I am, right?]

01:13:56.740 --> 01:13:57.740
You can't, right?

01:13:59.300 --> 01:14:04.500
The problem is he's leaving work so late.
[At that moment, Myungsoo appears from afar]

01:14:05.700 --> 01:14:07.380
[Is that him?]

01:14:08.140 --> 01:14:08.370
[Park Myungsoo] [Go Younjung]
[20m apart]

01:14:08.370 --> 01:14:12.030
There's no traffic now, so it'll only take 30 minutes. 30 minutes.

01:14:15.100 --> 01:14:15.860
[Polar Bear finally walks outside]

01:14:15.860 --> 01:14:17.250
Where is the car parked?

01:14:17.780 --> 01:14:20.820
[Park Myungsoo] [Go Younjung]
[Only 10m apart.]

01:14:20.820 --> 01:14:24.940
[Turns around]
[Park Myungsoo] [Go Younjung] [10m]

01:14:24.940 --> 01:14:28.420
[Park Myungsoo] [Go Younjung] [10m]
[Gasp... No!]

01:14:28.420 --> 01:14:33.900
[Park Myungsoo] [Go Younjung] [11m]
[He hasn't noticed at all]

01:14:33.900 --> 01:14:34.040
[Park Myungsoo] [Go Younjung] [11m]
[Myungsoo walks in the opposite direction]

01:14:34.040 --> 01:14:35.440
Turn left when you go out.

01:14:38.900 --> 01:14:42.500
[Park Myungsoo] [Go Younjung] [13m]
[I have to hurry, Kim Byunghyun is waiting.]

01:14:43.060 --> 01:14:45.140
[Go Younjung: Did he leave?]

01:14:45.860 --> 01:14:46.900
[Park Myungsoo]

01:14:47.700 --> 01:14:49.540
[Go Younjung]

01:14:50.540 --> 01:14:54.540
[Secretly watching Myungsoo as he walks away]

01:14:55.420 --> 01:15:01.500
[Attempting to approach again]
[Go Younjung]

01:15:03.860 --> 01:15:08.500
[Closing the distance]

01:15:11.100 --> 01:15:14.060
[However, after approaching cautiously...]

01:15:14.500 --> 01:15:17.330
[Myungsoo got in the car]
[Go Younjung]

01:15:17.330 --> 01:15:18.470
It's so cold.

01:15:20.780 --> 01:15:23.540
[Hurrying]

01:15:23.860 --> 01:15:24.270
[Preparing to set off]

01:15:24.270 --> 01:15:25.530
How do I drive this car?

01:15:28.620 --> 01:15:32.380
[Suddenly close]

01:15:33.780 --> 01:15:36.460
[Knock knock]

01:15:37.020 --> 01:15:42.420
[Approaching quietly]
[Thud] [Knock knock]

01:15:42.740 --> 01:15:46.180
[Runs away without looking back]

01:15:47.610 --> 01:15:50.210
That person just left. What am I supposed to do?

01:15:51.190 --> 01:15:51.260
This... wait a second. What is this?

01:15:51.260 --> 01:15:54.060
[Extremely panicked]

01:15:54.980 --> 01:15:57.180
[How can someone just leave something
on my car and run away!]

01:15:57.340 --> 01:16:00.820
[That's a gift]

01:16:01.660 --> 01:16:05.130
[Shrinking back after being bold]

01:16:05.380 --> 01:16:07.260
[Go Younjung: Well, my hands are shaking. My hands.]

01:16:07.260 --> 01:16:09.340
I feel like I'm literally going to die!

01:16:09.340 --> 01:16:12.470
[I think I've been caught...]

01:16:13.060 --> 01:16:18.450
[Peeking]
[Half worried, half curious about the reaction]

01:16:18.660 --> 01:16:22.650
[Not planning to catch her]
[Myungsoo opens the gift box]

01:16:22.680 --> 01:16:26.380
[Hello, Hyung. I've been your fan since Infinite Challenge.]

01:16:26.380 --> 01:16:29.780
[I'm honored and happy to meet you
through this opportunity.]

01:16:29.780 --> 01:16:33.180
[I also watch "Let's do it, Myungsoo."
Happy New Year!]

01:16:33.180 --> 01:16:34.240
[Hyung's Manito.]

01:16:34.240 --> 01:16:35.380
Wait a second. This...

01:16:35.380 --> 01:16:37.910
This doesn't look like a girl's handwriting.

01:16:38.340 --> 01:16:41.270
[Oh ho... why is it so... ha.
I don't understand this... ha.]

01:16:41.710 --> 01:16:41.860
I don't understand this.

01:16:41.860 --> 01:16:44.140
[Can you even deliver like this?]

01:16:44.140 --> 01:16:45.670
Wait a second. What is this?

01:16:46.040 --> 01:16:47.890
[A bread box for "Bread Myungsoo"]

01:16:47.890 --> 01:16:49.920
It's some snacks, cake,

01:16:50.690 --> 01:16:51.720
and bread.

01:16:51.720 --> 01:16:54.990
[Park Myungsoo: Bread...
How did they know I like bread?]

01:16:55.580 --> 01:16:57.980
[Someone left this here and ran!]
[The crew: Did you see them?]

01:16:58.020 --> 01:16:59.340
[No...]

01:16:59.340 --> 01:17:00.910
[Ah! I didn't see them!]

01:17:00.910 --> 01:17:02.050
It happened so fast.

01:17:02.180 --> 01:17:03.780
[Truly didn't see]
[It's a man. A man! A man! A man!]

01:17:03.780 --> 01:17:05.400
It must be a man.

01:17:06.880 --> 01:17:09.960
[Oh, bread! These are all my favorites!]

01:17:10.040 --> 01:17:11.200
It's all snacks.

01:17:11.200 --> 01:17:12.220
[Hey, damn it!]

01:17:12.220 --> 01:17:12.660
It's so cold, the snacks are frozen stiff.

01:17:12.660 --> 01:17:14.960
[My precious bread must be freezing.]

01:17:14.960 --> 01:17:17.260
It's -16 degrees right now.

01:17:17.260 --> 01:17:18.020
Bringing this all the way here...

01:17:18.020 --> 01:17:19.320
[Acting tough because he is secretly thrilled]

01:17:19.320 --> 01:17:21.970
Even though they brought this, it's freezing!

01:17:22.820 --> 01:17:26.920
[Oh, seriously.]

01:17:28.020 --> 01:17:33.590
[Go Younjung: So there should be a message now
saying the gift was received?]

01:17:35.900 --> 01:17:36.630
Whoa.

01:17:37.650 --> 01:17:38.230
A message like this came.

01:17:38.230 --> 01:17:40.040
[Satisfied]

01:17:40.040 --> 01:17:40.860
Ah, really.

01:17:41.250 --> 01:17:42.780
This is really satisfying.

01:17:43.560 --> 01:17:45.890
[At that time, Myungsoo pours
all his attention into the bread]

01:17:45.890 --> 01:17:46.690
Wait a second.

01:17:47.620 --> 01:17:48.730
Wait a second.

01:17:49.350 --> 01:17:49.420
Every single bread has a cartoon sticker of me on it!

01:17:49.420 --> 01:17:51.950
[Discovers the cartoon stickers on every bread]

01:17:51.950 --> 01:17:53.010
Like this.

01:17:54.580 --> 01:17:58.000
[So touched]
[They sincerely put a sticker
on every single one.]

01:17:58.300 --> 01:18:01.140
[Dubai! Who! Who! What is this!]

01:18:01.140 --> 01:18:03.900
Isn't this a Dubai cookie?

01:18:04.460 --> 01:18:05.460
What is this?

01:18:05.460 --> 01:18:08.870
[This time, taking a bite
as soon as he sees it]

01:18:09.630 --> 01:18:11.540
[This looks like those Dubai Cookies.]

01:18:11.900 --> 01:18:14.370
[Munch munch]

01:18:14.610 --> 01:18:14.700
These are hard to buy.

01:18:14.700 --> 01:18:17.390
[These are hard to buy.]

01:18:17.900 --> 01:18:21.000
[Meanwhile, Younjung catches her breath]

01:18:21.300 --> 01:18:26.180
[Go Younjung: I underestimated this.
Tomorrow and the day after,]

01:18:26.180 --> 01:18:26.600
I need to eat a full breakfast before I come.

01:18:26.600 --> 01:18:28.980
[I need to eat a full breakfast before I come.]

01:18:28.990 --> 01:18:30.040
I ran away the moment I put it on the windshield.

01:18:30.040 --> 01:18:32.890
[But she regains energy talking about the gift]

01:18:32.890 --> 01:18:35.490
But after the gift is received,

01:18:35.490 --> 01:18:37.300
my dopamine is through the roof.

01:18:37.490 --> 01:18:40.880
[So much fun! So much fun! So much fun!]

01:18:41.230 --> 01:18:44.860
[Handmade]
[Jinkyung prepared home-brewed alcohol
and a famous quote scroll]

01:18:45.200 --> 01:18:48.230
[Hong Jinkyung: This is a poem by Mr. Jeong Yakyong—]

01:18:48.660 --> 01:18:49.190
[Drinking on a Moonlit Night. Plus a poem by an ancestor.]
[Source: Dasan Memorial Hall]

01:18:49.190 --> 01:18:51.030
I will write it on this.

01:18:53.110 --> 01:18:55.400
[Drinking on a Moonlit Night.]

01:18:55.740 --> 01:18:57.600
[Focused]

01:18:57.680 --> 01:18:57.880
While drinking...

01:18:57.880 --> 01:19:03.010
[Drinking on a Moonlit Night.]
[Hey, I want to drink while watching the moon.]
[Surprisingly beautiful handwriting]

01:19:04.860 --> 01:19:10.060
[Don't miss tonight when the moon rises.]

01:19:10.660 --> 01:19:10.760
[Hope Manito Hae-in won't miss
this moonlit night either]

01:19:10.760 --> 01:19:13.950
Amazing. Mr. Jeong Yakyong is so cool.

01:19:13.950 --> 01:19:15.350
The poem is wonderful.

01:19:17.580 --> 01:19:19.530
[Cough cough... cough cough!]

01:19:19.750 --> 01:19:19.770
Let's add more before we go.

01:19:19.770 --> 01:19:22.700
[Let's add some balloons
to bulk up the gifts before we head out.]

01:19:23.430 --> 01:19:26.800
[Adding more gifts]
[Searching for balloon art]

01:19:27.300 --> 01:19:31.160
[Hahaha, there's a lion! A lion!]

01:19:31.430 --> 01:19:33.980
[Feeling slightly regretful,
taking a balloon art lesson on the street]

01:19:34.250 --> 01:19:36.920
[Focused]

01:19:37.230 --> 01:19:39.320
[Just pump 30cm of air in.]

01:19:39.320 --> 01:19:40.230
It'll be a lion, a bit bigger than this.

01:19:40.230 --> 01:19:44.580
[Today's wind chill in Seoul is -20 degrees]

01:19:45.050 --> 01:19:48.140
[But you can't have an invitation
without balloons...]

01:19:48.140 --> 01:19:49.800
I have to draw a face on it.

01:19:50.080 --> 01:19:51.290
This morning, my grandmother told me

01:19:51.290 --> 01:19:52.990
[The Dahan that Grandma warned about]

01:19:52.990 --> 01:19:55.390
today is Dahan, the coldest day of the year.

01:19:56.170 --> 01:19:56.760
[Passion for the Manito gift defeats the cold]

01:19:56.760 --> 01:19:58.180
Twist five or six of them.

01:20:01.580 --> 01:20:04.960
[Ah, wait. My hands hurt so much from the cold.]

01:20:05.350 --> 01:20:09.190
[Luckily, I brought the leftover heat packs]

01:20:09.700 --> 01:20:12.460
[Kim Dohoon: OK! I'll try to do it.]

01:20:12.920 --> 01:20:16.440
[Starting his first-ever balloon art]

01:20:16.980 --> 01:20:20.730
[Why does the balloon look so ugly
when it's inflated?]

01:20:21.260 --> 01:20:22.260
Well.

01:20:22.880 --> 01:20:27.520
[In the freezing weather,
even tying a knot isn't easy]

01:20:28.620 --> 01:20:28.650
[Endless rewinds]

01:20:28.650 --> 01:20:30.300
Wait for me, Teacher.

01:20:33.430 --> 01:20:34.830
[How do you make it like that?]

01:20:34.830 --> 01:20:35.140
I can't do it like that, Teacher.

01:20:35.140 --> 01:20:37.870
[Teacher… this is way too fast...]

01:20:38.340 --> 01:20:40.500
[The long and difficult road of handmade crafting]

01:20:40.500 --> 01:20:42.130
It's really hard.

01:20:42.450 --> 01:20:43.920
How do I make this?

01:20:43.920 --> 01:20:45.080
Seriously.

01:20:45.740 --> 01:20:50.410
[Frustrated]

01:20:51.590 --> 01:20:56.680
[Starting to get the hang
of balloon art after several trials]

01:20:58.210 --> 01:21:01.750
[Senior, I'm sorry. This is what I made.]

01:21:02.080 --> 01:21:05.800
[I couldn't do any better...] [Shivers]

01:21:05.800 --> 01:21:05.940
[Lion] [Pig]
[A somewhat rough lion and a pig]

01:21:05.940 --> 01:21:08.080
This is a lion. This is a pig.

01:21:09.540 --> 01:21:11.530
[Hong Jinkyung: For Hae-in's location,
let's head to the big department store first.]

01:21:11.530 --> 01:21:12.800
[I have a face mask and stuff.]

01:21:12.800 --> 01:21:13.660
I'll do it like this.

01:21:13.660 --> 01:21:16.240
[Wearing a mask and sunglasses
must make me stand out, right?]

01:21:16.240 --> 01:21:16.700
But...

01:21:17.030 --> 01:21:18.840
[I'll lower my height]

01:21:19.020 --> 01:21:21.720
[and wear a coat!
Then he won't know it's me!]

01:21:21.720 --> 01:21:22.130
I'll try it out first.

01:21:22.130 --> 01:21:24.270
[Tall person]
[Eliminating the most "Hong Jinkyung" features first]

01:21:24.270 --> 01:21:25.640
He won't know it's me.

01:21:29.490 --> 01:21:32.150
[A rising black soul]

01:21:32.150 --> 01:21:33.410
Could you tell it's me?

01:21:34.120 --> 01:21:36.220
[It doesn't look like Hong Jinkyung this way, right?]

01:21:37.300 --> 01:21:39.860
[He won't know it's Hong Jinkyung...
but you'll stand out more because it's weird...]

01:21:39.860 --> 01:21:40.980
Look.

01:21:41.180 --> 01:21:42.730
[No one knows who it is, right?]

01:21:42.800 --> 01:21:43.050
No one knows, right?

01:21:43.050 --> 01:21:45.560
[Pressure]

01:21:45.920 --> 01:21:47.750
[Should I walk like this instead?]

01:21:48.100 --> 01:21:49.970
[Walking on knees]

01:21:49.970 --> 01:21:51.310
Truly unrecognizable.

01:21:52.000 --> 01:21:53.800
[I really will stay low like this!]

01:21:54.080 --> 01:21:55.300
[What if he chases you?]

01:21:55.300 --> 01:21:56.890
[Then I'll run like this!]

01:21:57.770 --> 01:22:01.290
[Waddle] [Waddle]

01:22:02.760 --> 01:22:04.320
[Exhausted]

01:22:04.390 --> 01:22:04.770
Walking like this is too tiring.

01:22:04.770 --> 01:22:07.410
[While Jinkyung simulates her escape...]

01:22:07.760 --> 01:22:10.550
[Dohoon heads to Jinkyung's house]

01:22:10.840 --> 01:22:14.660
[The goal is to ring the doorbell,
run away, and take a "paparazzi" photo]

01:22:15.210 --> 01:22:15.250
Let's go. Moving out.

01:22:15.250 --> 01:22:17.700
[Before leaving,
Jinkyung tries to hide her height]

01:22:18.240 --> 01:22:23.010
[Dohoon approaching stealthily]

01:22:24.080 --> 01:22:28.830
[The two separated by the entrance door]

01:22:31.480 --> 01:22:33.720
[Rings the doorbell and runs]

01:22:34.760 --> 01:22:36.100
[Who is it?]

01:22:36.100 --> 01:22:36.720
Who is it?

01:22:40.260 --> 01:22:42.740
[Jinkyung walking outside]

01:22:43.110 --> 01:22:46.650
[Have to reach the photo spot
before Jinkyung comes out!]

01:22:50.870 --> 01:22:52.560
[What is this?]

01:22:52.800 --> 01:22:52.970
What is this?

01:22:52.970 --> 01:22:56.150
[Discovers the gift]

01:22:56.840 --> 01:22:59.440
[Whoa, amazing! Did Pig send this to me?]

01:23:00.080 --> 01:23:04.100
[Click]
[Luckily reached the photo spot just in time]

01:23:04.750 --> 01:23:05.650
[Click]

01:23:05.650 --> 01:23:08.510
[Took an atmospheric paparazzi photo]

01:23:10.050 --> 01:23:10.100
[A long handwritten letter with the gift]

01:23:10.100 --> 01:23:12.500
I feel like I should use a box like this, too.

01:23:14.960 --> 01:23:16.640
[Seeing how you can pull off anything you wear]

01:23:16.640 --> 01:23:19.490
[and always take on diverse styles,]

01:23:19.760 --> 01:23:22.300
[I prepared a bag to warm up this chilly day.]

01:23:22.520 --> 01:23:25.760
[And I want to prepare an even
warmer gift for you tomorrow.]

01:23:25.930 --> 01:23:28.630
[This is the Manito Club's first gift invitation.
If you accept the invitation, bring this letter.]

01:23:28.630 --> 01:23:29.000
If you decline, leave the letter at the door.

01:23:29.000 --> 01:23:32.200
[If you decline, leave the letter at the door.]

01:23:32.370 --> 01:23:36.080
[But I really want to invite you. Please... accept...]
[Filled with earnestness...]

01:23:36.400 --> 01:23:38.590
[From your Manito who wants to see you very, very much.]

01:23:39.320 --> 01:23:40.930
[Hahaha. Hahaha.]

01:23:41.070 --> 01:23:43.470
[So cute]

01:23:43.850 --> 01:23:45.700
[Who is it?]

01:23:46.180 --> 01:23:48.580
[Hong Jinkyung: Wow... what a quirky person.]

01:23:49.080 --> 01:23:51.420
[Hong Jinkyung: It's a bag. A truly warm bag.]

01:23:56.240 --> 01:24:00.710
[My back feels as warm as lying on a heated floor.]

01:24:01.150 --> 01:24:02.540
[My back feels like it's being grilled.]

01:24:02.600 --> 01:24:02.810
It's so warm. Incredible.

01:24:02.810 --> 01:24:05.240
[Satisfied]

01:24:05.610 --> 01:24:08.700
[A direct hit to her preference]

01:24:08.700 --> 01:24:09.840
Amazing.

01:24:11.310 --> 01:24:14.050
[Thanks to this bag, I definitely won't be cold.]

01:24:14.560 --> 01:24:17.610
[So cold.]

01:24:17.780 --> 01:24:17.930
The camera won't turn on because it's too cold.

01:24:17.930 --> 01:24:21.580
[Due to the cold, both the
camera and Dohoon are frozen]

01:24:21.950 --> 01:24:25.350
[Hong Jinkyung: First of all,
I'm so satisfied with this bag.]

01:24:25.570 --> 01:24:27.730
[This cleverness is so cute.]

01:24:27.950 --> 01:24:29.420
[I have to wear it when I go out]

01:24:32.060 --> 01:24:32.080
This Manito is a bit clumsy.

01:24:32.080 --> 01:24:34.020
[Cute but a bit clumsy...]

01:24:34.440 --> 01:24:37.010
[Fixing it herself]

01:24:37.300 --> 01:24:39.280
[I don't know who it is, but it's really novel.]

01:24:39.280 --> 01:24:41.010
My back is so warm.

01:24:42.390 --> 01:24:45.870
[A very, very quirky Manito.]

01:24:46.260 --> 01:24:49.000
[So cute. Who is Pig?]

01:24:52.030 --> 01:24:55.320
[Oh, I think the Pig is really funny.]

01:24:55.970 --> 01:24:59.930
[Kim Dohoon: I'll go check the invitation first.]

01:25:00.710 --> 01:25:04.370
[Did Jinkyung accept the invitation?]

01:25:06.620 --> 01:25:11.450
[Looking left and right]

01:25:11.720 --> 01:25:11.900
[Checked everywhere...]

01:25:11.900 --> 01:25:13.060
Nothing. Nothing.

01:25:13.450 --> 01:25:15.350
[Nothing! ]
[She took it! She took it!]

01:25:15.650 --> 01:25:15.820
She took it.

01:25:15.820 --> 01:25:20.070
[Invitation successful]
[She's coming tomorrow!]

01:25:20.310 --> 01:25:22.720
[So happy, he's writing another letter]

01:25:23.160 --> 01:25:29.310
[See you tomorrow.]

01:25:29.750 --> 01:25:32.940
[Though I couldn't invite you boldly
and powerfully]

01:25:33.350 --> 01:25:33.800
[See you tomorrow—Your Exclusive Manito.]
[Doing his best to emphasize tomorrow's gift]

01:25:33.800 --> 01:25:35.640
Done. Done.

01:25:37.800 --> 01:25:40.580
[See you tomorrow.]

01:25:41.240 --> 01:25:43.790
[Meanwhile, at HQ]

01:25:44.110 --> 01:25:44.210
You have been invited to the "Manito Club."

01:25:44.210 --> 01:25:46.670
[Secretly sending out an invitation]

01:25:46.670 --> 01:25:47.060
Hello, this is a flash delivery.

01:25:47.060 --> 01:25:50.510
[Benefit for the first gift-giver]

01:25:50.660 --> 01:25:52.690
This time, the hidden Manito of the Manito Club...

01:25:52.690 --> 01:25:54.640
[The hidden Manito appears]

01:25:55.050 --> 01:25:57.700
[See you tomorrow, Hyung.]

01:25:58.520 --> 01:26:01.690
[Code Name: Catfish.]

01:26:01.700 --> 01:26:01.790
[Bulking up]
[New use for forearm muscles]

01:26:01.790 --> 01:26:03.280
Forearm muscles are meant for times like this.

01:26:03.280 --> 01:26:04.270
Bulking up.

01:26:04.340 --> 01:26:06.400
[They're pumped up now, hahaha.]
[What is the true nature of the "bulking up" gift?]

01:26:06.870 --> 01:26:08.290
[I'm making Dubai chewy cookies.]

01:26:08.320 --> 01:26:08.470
I never thought I'd be making these.

01:26:08.470 --> 01:26:09.630
[Unexpected handmade crafting]

01:26:09.630 --> 01:26:11.710
[Giving Dubai chewy cookies]

01:26:11.740 --> 01:26:13.080
[The texture is interesting.]

01:26:13.160 --> 01:26:13.260
Giving a gift that the other person might like

01:26:13.260 --> 01:26:14.720
[Feeling the joy of giving once again]

01:26:14.720 --> 01:26:16.100
is a happy thing in itself.

01:26:16.100 --> 01:26:18.230
You're watching, right? Go Younjung.

01:26:18.300 --> 01:26:18.740
But I want to submit a letter.

01:26:18.740 --> 01:26:20.270
[Wanting to submit to Myungsoo's radio show]

01:26:20.310 --> 01:26:20.480
Hello, I'm DJ G-Park.

01:26:20.480 --> 01:26:23.150
[Will this submission make it on air?]

01:26:23.150 --> 01:26:24.400
[Hello, Park Myungsoo!]

01:26:24.670 --> 01:26:26.240
[Hello, Park Myungsoo! I'm an old fan of yours.
I want to send the favorite bread of the hyung I like,
so I traveled all over Seoul in -10 degree weather.
I hope this sincerity definitely reached him.
He probably has no idea who it is, right?
If he hears this radio,
I hope he takes care of his health!
—Secret Hee-do.]

01:26:26.240 --> 01:26:28.660
[Hello, Park Myungsoo! I'm an old fan of yours.
I want to send the favorite bread
of the hyung I like...]

01:26:28.660 --> 01:26:30.300
[In -10 degree weather...]

01:26:30.300 --> 01:26:31.350
[It was you!]

01:26:31.350 --> 01:26:32.490
[My Manito, you came!]

01:26:32.490 --> 01:26:33.050
[That person! That person! That person!]

01:26:33.050 --> 01:26:35.340
[Oh! That person just came in!]
[Spotting the Manito's raid]

01:26:35.410 --> 01:26:36.280
They are definitely hiding somewhere.

01:26:36.280 --> 01:26:37.100
[From your Secret Heedo.]
[How deep is Younjung's infiltration?]

01:26:37.100 --> 01:26:38.730
Secret Heedo.

01:26:40.490 --> 01:26:41.330
Hyung, do you usually eat well?

01:26:41.330 --> 01:26:43.020
[Hidden Manito Catfish appears]

01:26:43.020 --> 01:26:43.250
[Oppa, I made this myself.] [Hae-in Oppa.]
[Catfish joins to stir things up]

01:26:43.250 --> 01:26:44.480
Hae-in Oppa.

01:26:45.240 --> 01:26:45.480
Hae-in, what's going on?

01:26:45.480 --> 01:26:46.800
[And Hae-in's old friend]

01:26:46.800 --> 01:26:47.820
You can't see my face, right?

01:26:47.820 --> 01:26:48.070
Do I have two Manitos?

01:26:48.070 --> 01:26:48.980
[Two Manitos?]

01:26:48.980 --> 01:26:51.380
[Handmade gifts for Hae-in by two people]

01:26:51.380 --> 01:26:55.260
[Hae-in's photoshoot set]
[Two Manitos gathered in the same place]

01:26:55.920 --> 01:26:56.550
[Sensing something suspicious]

01:26:56.550 --> 01:26:57.840
[What is this?]

01:26:57.840 --> 01:27:01.020
[Clatter]
[The prelude to the Great Hae-in Showdown]

01:27:01.020 --> 01:27:02.020
[Peeking]
[The prelude to the Great Hae-in Showdown]

01:27:04.620 --> 01:27:05.670
[Run if you don't want to be caught]

01:27:05.670 --> 01:27:07.930
I was so startled.

01:27:08.150 --> 01:27:10.170
Alright. Alright. Alright.

01:27:10.170 --> 01:27:11.010
Where are they?

01:27:11.010 --> 01:27:12.660
That's strange.

01:27:12.660 --> 01:27:14.020
I feel like someone is here.

01:27:14.020 --> 01:27:15.300
[That's insane. Dopamine overload.]
[Another person hiding along with Jinkyung]

01:27:15.300 --> 01:27:16.460
[Get ready to run]
[Another person hiding along with Jinkyung]

01:27:16.460 --> 01:27:18.900
[Isn't that Jinkyung?]
[Dohoon joins in, too]

01:27:20.100 --> 01:27:20.170
[Manitos appearing in large numbers simultaneously]
[A crazy party]

01:27:20.170 --> 01:27:23.000
Why does he keep chasing me? I'm going crazy.

01:27:23.780 --> 01:27:25.190
What's going on?

01:27:25.190 --> 01:27:25.460
What's going on?

01:27:25.460 --> 01:27:27.610
[What is the outcome of the Great Hae-in Showdown?]